name: Brittleblast
flavorText: "When Skaði exhales, a warrior is forced to adapt, but the obstinate man simply shatters." -Einherjar proverb

name: Glory Seeker
flavorText: Once living fall silent, the dead can find a terrible comfort in standing alone.

name: Lookie
flavorText: What's the good word, Lou; you get a peek at what we're up against?

name: Rebel Roughrider
flavorText: Those rebels hiding out in the chop shop gave me some wicked ideas for souping up my ride.

name: Winter's Bite
flavorText: Allow me to demonstrate why pushing this far into Einherjar territory wasn't such a hot idea...

name: Black Box Operator
flavorText: "Monitoring outputs is taking too long," I'll show them; I've got yer system access right here!

name: Knoll of Conquest
flavorText: A fitting battlefield then, if indeed it was the bacl of a great fallen Jotun.

name: Elemental Fortification
flavorText: No idea what to give a stone person as a thank-you gift, but that's right neighborly.

name: Hydrophonic Hank
flavorText: Audio-neural-link = clean; start(data dive)

name: Shaterstone Palace
flavorText: Even concrete is made up of tiny elemental chunks.

name: Valr Smith
flavorText: The irony of finding my life's calling after dying isn't lost on me.

name: Primeval Son
flavorText: The essence of Ymir exists in the bones of everything.

name: Berserkgangr
flavorText: They fear our anger because the strength of our convictions is infectious.

name: Eagle Scout
flavorText: They're using some sort of cloaking technique, but we've got eyes on the target.

name: Oversight Surge
flavorText: Given the speed and success of the athletic trials, I'm afraid research funding for this method of enhancement is being cut.

name: Thunderbird Egg
flavorText: Which came first, the incubator or 220 volts of electricity?

name: Enlistment Bonus
flavorText: Magpyre's private military recruitment drive is in full swing, promising to turn Mesoamerican youth into Aztlan might.

name: Grit Instructor
flavorText:
From now on telpochalli child, your name is Try or Die.  
Try or Die, drop and give me twenty!

name: River of Winged Snake
flavorText: The runoff from the binary xiik's facilities was proven to be perfectly save, and even arguably beneficial for certain emergent downriver species.

name: Ayotl Vanguard
flavorText: Agitated?  Escalation isn't the way; try Serentix today!

name: Yara from Arawaka
flavorText: Oho!  Another fascinating discovery...

name: Shuar Stalker
flavorText: I think something's following us... was that a hiss or a growl?

name: A34 Jaguar
flavorText: Soldiers respond better when protected by animal-form automatons than human shaped units.

name: Harpy-One
flavorText: Target has been neutralized with extreme prejudice.

name: Oh Fortuitous Find!
flavorText: True happiness is solid fieldwork

name: A56 Ahtatl
flavorText: We'll be ready sir; it's going to take more than a few malcontents to disrupt operations.

name: Lady in the Water
flavorText: The legend of Yacumama is real... I'm guessing para-sailing is cancelled.

name: Carny Rioter
flavorText: This was a peaceful protest until they broke out the tear gas.

name: Sunken Acolyte
flavorText: You were born from water, and life is prepared for a grand return to the seas

name: Algosian Mask
flavorText: We mistook our blessings for curses because our thinking was limited; Before Her, we didn't think of pain as a resource.

name: Drowned Observatory
flavorText: A glimpse of His prison changes us all in different ways, but to the same ends.

name: There is No Safe Word
flavorText: If you have to ask, darling, I'm afraid you're already in over your head.

name: Venal Equinox
flavorText: See that you gallop toward a future that is free of tyranny.

name: Driven Lyric
flavorText:
As if you hate dancing and the divine 
 Rebel rebel, torn asunder 
 Hot damn, but it makes you wonder

name: Threnody Muse
flavorText: I am haunted, driven by memories of compositions that failed to inspire the kind of change that's now needed.

name: Caryatid of the Vault
flavorText: Working defense contracts for a decade, and you'd think I'd have seen just about every layer of security there is.

name: Saltwater Empousa
flavorText: The tendrils of his inspiration can reach anyone; in absence, he is everywhere.

name: Sir Shaggy the Brave
flavorText: No one needed to train him; if anything he's got US trained to charge in there after him!

name: Vault of the Oberos
flavorText: Clients enjoy peace of mind, whether their assets are solid, liquid, or virtual.

name: Vestai Virago
flavorText: If you're going to treat yourself, you might as well treat yourself right.

name: Whispers of the Profane
flavorText: For all that claim to hear Him in the tides, those who truly listen get to become part of His vast design.

name: The Bastard of Autolycus
flavorText: My dear, for you I would steal the earth itself just to sweep you off your feet.

name: Æther Engineer
flavorText: These bonds are messed up; someone needs to teach those werewolves to weld.

name: Dreni Propogandist
flavorText: To control a populace, one must control the message.

name: Sett Borsuk
flavorText: You really think I give a Rat's arse?  After everything that was taken from us, it's hard to care.

name: Volkov Induction
flavorText: It will be a day of pain... but also excitement and joy; after today, you are a member of the Great Pack!

name: Merry Prankster
flavorText: Oooh what'cha doin' there?  What's that button do?  Can I press it?

name: Vodnik Junker
flavorText: You haul it in, we break it down; no questions asked!

name: War Documentarian
flavorText: Multiple radical groups are thought to be behind this terrorist action in progress...

name: Grigori Protocol
flavorText: I award you the ternal star for your distinction in service to the Dreni cause.

name: Ved'ma Steelshaper
flavorText: These cowards like hiding almost as much as I enjoy practice.

name: Veela Spy
flavorText: These days, loose lips might not be enough to sink ships...

name: White Tower Warden
flavorText: Quickly now.  I assure you, the covens have no sway over this grove.

name: Terminal Calculus
flavorText: Well, if you hate my love of math so much why don't you just cease to exist?

name: Vortex Hovertank
flavorText: ...And speaking of distractions, their heavy reinforcements have arrived.  Fantastic.

name: Khyber Outcast
flavorText: When merely sharing the air with Parsa became painful, that was when we realized that Bab-Rmal was no longer our home.

name: Sovereign Blessing
flavorText: By extended provision of the Merkabic sublaw; may mortal blood be of seraphic need, transient energies must be lent freely if returned.

name: Ilanot of He That Is
flavorText: You'd be paranoid too if your antiques could be reality binding contracts.

name: Spire of Sand and Glass
flavorText: When the sun rises over them you'll see why they call it 'the beacon city.'

name: Xerxian Agitator
flavorText: Our cause grows with every meeting, and I find that we're more alike than anyone would have guessed.

name: More than Protect
flavorText: If the Empress won't listen, we will go where our voices will be heard!

name: Si'lat Elite
flavorText: Did someone straight up collapse at the rave last night?  Must have been intense!

name: Xerxian Insurrectionist
flavorText: Despite the risk, these missings are about creating bonds between our disparate forces; the sabotage is merely a bonus.

name: Khyber Qomandan
flavorText: Believe it or not, 'the rebel godmothers' used to be Parsa's toughest field commanders.

name: Parsa's Cornucopia
flavorText: Your labor, and your loyalty; a small price to pay for the infinite bounty we are offering.

name: Shackle
flavorText: Excellent work, Ariel.  Inform our Ved'ma contact that we've got their wayward countryman.

name: Shaitan Pariah
flavorText: Beings of magic aren't just interested in the properties of matter, they're interested in matters of property.

name: Arcanovore
flavorText: Between horn poaching and most magic becoming cast instead of raw, I really feel for them.

name: He Who Creates
flavorText: If a lithe body of ceramic, silicon, and steel is such a wonder to behold, then imagine the joy of shaping it!

name: Inked Brawler
flavorText: Respect our existence or respect resistance.

name: Overtime Affliction
flavorText: I can't remember my family's faces... where do I live, did I already pass away?

name: Trusty Hireling
flavorText: Oh no, thank YOU sir, always a pleasure to bear the loot of a living legend!

name: Family Ties
flavorText: Those corporate dogs will pay for what has transpired here.

name: Sister Spitfire
flavorText: You gotta be a bit of a hothead to make it, out here.

name: White Metal Ox
flavorText: If this is some sort of publicity stunt, those energy drink corporations have officially gone too far!

name: Brother Moonblade
flavorText: If the rebels have managed to reach even us, then you shouldn't question their grasp.

name: House of a Thousand Grudges
flavorText: We figured the witches and their dogs couldn't find us inside... but something else did.

name: Koga Impostor
flavorText: If I can just get this intel out of Harmony territory, it will all be worth it...

name: Mirror Pack
flavorText: It's not illegal per se, but the dupes won't always shift between realms cleanly.

name: Comb Trader
flavorText: We wouldn't want your follicles to become horribly tangled now, would we?

name: Take to the Streets
flavorText: We've brought warring gangs together before; sometimes to get people on the same page you've just got to knock some sense into everyone.

name: Dragon Slayer
flavorText: Don't hate the player OR the game; hate on all the DKP I just ganked from ya!

name: Forbidden Floors
flavorText: Headed down?

name: Vendomomo
flavorText: Aw, it's adorable!  Go on, I think it wants you to buy something.

name: Anthem of the Rebellion
flavorText: It gets under your skin, right?  Like everyone in power wants us to shut up and stop thinking about it?

name: Imugi of Good Fortune
flavorText: We're all beholden to the ebb and flow of prsoperity, from bacteria to celestial beings.

name: Triforge Alliance
flavorText: Structure.  Progress.  Vision.

name: Corporate Confab
flavorText: Well, you consulted the right people on this.  We can grow exponentially, where Parsan manufacturing only scales linearly with golem size.

name: Cyberminotar
flavorText: Lest we forget that great gear really makes the monster, not just the man.

name: Angelischism
flavorText: "She cannot see through your burdens, and will never truly know you; the only way to break your contracts is to give us the boy and become the champion everyone needs."
